children.name: 7.2.0 User with the admin role, can login to content management platform with the same credentials as for the mob app
7.3.0 User with the admin role, can log out from the CMS
7.4.0 User with the admin role, can have access to profile page and edit profile information
7.5.0 User with the admin role can reset password from the CMS login page
2.2.0 As a user, I want to log in with my email and password
2.3.0 As a user I want to reset my password if I forget it
2.4.0 As a user, I want to stay logged in for as long as possible, so that I don't have to log in frequently
2.5.0 As a user, I want to log out and log back in
2.5.0 As a user, I want to be able to log out from the app
3.2.0 As a registered user I can view and update my bio
3.3.0 As a registered user I can view and update profile image
3.4.0 As a registered user I can view and update my profile settings
3.5.0 As a registered user I can add my kids info in my profile page
3.7.0 As a registered user I can edit my current stage
4.2.0 As a user during onboarding, I should be able to start one of the recommended programs right from the onboarding
4.3.0 As a user on the home page I should be able to see the list of recommended programs
4.5.0 As a user I can enroll/unenroll any of the programs
4.8.0 As a user I should be able to check programs details
4.10.0 As a user I should be able to make progress in the program by completing each step of it
14.1.0 As a user, I want to join a community based on my selected stage during onboarding.
14.2.0 As a user I want to create text or text + image posts to share with the community
14.4.0 As a user, I want to interact with post: 'Like' post, leave comments
16.2.0 As a user, I want an in-app notifications page, so that I can view all my missed notifications in one place, even if I missed the initial push notification.
